genresAdvancedInfo.name: slovenian electronic
genresAdvancedInfo.description: Slovenian electronic music is a blend of traditional Slovenian folk music and modern electronic beats. It incorporates elements of techno, house, and trance, and often features accordion and other folk instruments. Slovenian electronic music is known for its high energy and danceable rhythms, and is popular in clubs and festivals throughout Slovenia and Europe.
